	(text "As pointed in this video https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TpXvac1Y3h0,\ntwo big capacitors has a better frequency response than a big and small one.\nThe OUT3 and OUT4 are just me playing with it.\n\nThe data taken from the Murata site:\nhttps://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/e/2PACX-1vSXia0E0twhmxxn8AhihW4_F9pXLQ8qSpSzaD45WeS-rncIm1tf8ZpPtWoLQ9H4OztY1IgeKpUjvDQX/pubhtml"
